name: 透の母
text: お母さん買い物に行くけど、来るー？
trans: Mom's gonna go shopping, are you coming?

name: 透の母
text: でも、みんなも今日出かけてるんでしょー？
trans: Everyone's going to be out today, you know?

name: 透
trans:
It's okay.
I'll go to the park.

name: 透の母
text:
そー
気を付けてねー
trans:
Is that so.
Take care of yourself, alright?

name: 近所の子
text:
っていうかさー
ジャングルジムってつまんなくない？
trans:
I mean like,
don't you get bored of the jungle gym?

name: 近所の子
trans: All you do is just climb it.

name: 透
trans: All you do is just, climb it──

name: 近所の子
text: ねー、あっちで一緒に遊ぼーよ
trans: C'moon, let's go play together over thereee.

name: 透
text:
あ、ごめん
僕、もう帰る
trans:
Ah, sorry.
I'm gonna go home.

name: 学生
text:
ああ、ここだ
間に合ったかな……
trans:
Ahh, it's here.
I wonder if I made it in time...

name: 透
text:
歩いた方が早いよ
駅でしょ
trans:
It's faster if you walk from here. 
You're going to the station, right?

name: 学生
trans:
...Eh?
──Ah... The bus won't be here till a while, huh.

name: 透
trans: I felt like I was almost there.
